{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":799,"text":"This picture"},{"time":2699,"text":"is from my metro card"},{"time":4373,"text":"when I spent a year abroad in Paris\nin college in the mid-'90s."},{"time":8799,"text":"My friend says I look\nlike a French anarchist --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":11994,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":13025,"text":"But this is still what I see"},{"time":14396,"text":"when I look in the mirror in the morning."},{"time":16587,"text":"Within a month of living in Paris,\nI'd lost 15 pounds"},{"time":19710,"text":"and I was in the best shape of my life"},{"time":21769,"text":"because I was eating fresh food"},{"time":23790,"text":"and I was walking wherever I went."}]},{"cues":[{"time":26828,"text":"Having grown up in suburban Atlanta,"},{"time":28663,"text":"a region built largely\nby highways and automobiles"},{"time":32092,"text":"and with a reputation\nas a poster child for sprawl,"},{"time":35777,"text":"Paris fundamentally changed\nthe way I understood"},{"time":38363,"text":"the construction of the world around me,"},{"time":41107,"text":"and I got obsessed with the role\nof infrastructure --"},{"time":44619,"text":"that it's not just the way to move people\nfrom point A to point B,"},{"time":48737,"text":"it's not just the way to convey water\nor sewage or energy,"},{"time":52850,"text":"but it's the foundation for our economy."},{"time":55444,"text":"It's the foundation for our social life\nand for our culture,"},{"time":58831,"text":"and it really matters\nto the way that we live."}]},{"cues":[{"time":62118,"text":"When I came home,\nI was instantly frustrated,"},{"time":64726,"text":"stuck in traffic as I crossed\nthe top end of our perimeter highway."},{"time":68676,"text":"Not only was I not moving a muscle,"},{"time":70967,"text":"I had no social interaction"},{"time":72636,"text":"with the hundreds of thousands of people\nthat were hurtling past me,"},{"time":75899,"text":"like me, with their eyes faced forward\nand their music blaring."},{"time":80765,"text":"I wondered if this was\nan inevitable outcome,"},{"time":83586,"text":"or could we do something about it."},{"time":85817,"text":"Was it possible to transform\nthis condition in Atlanta"},{"time":89069,"text":"into the kind of place\nthat I wanted to live in?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":91949,"text":"I went back to grad school\nin architecture and city planning,"},{"time":95069,"text":"developed this interest in infrastructure,"},{"time":97425,"text":"and in 1999 came up with an idea"},{"time":100042,"text":"for my thesis project:"},{"time":101631,"text":"the adaptation of an obsolete loop\nof old railroad circling downtown"},{"time":105972,"text":"as a new infrastructure\nfor urban revitalization."},{"time":109036,"text":"It was just an idea."},{"time":110800,"text":"I never thought\nwe would actually build it."},{"time":114215,"text":"But I went to work\nat an architecture firm,"},{"time":116723,"text":"and eventually talked\nto my coworkers about it,"},{"time":119270,"text":"and they loved the idea."},{"time":121062,"text":"And as we started talking\nto more people about it,"},{"time":123472,"text":"more people wanted to hear about it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":125889,"text":"In the summer of 2001,"},{"time":128269,"text":"we connected with Cathy Woolard,"},{"time":129920,"text":"who was soon elected\ncity council president."},{"time":132075,"text":"And we built a citywide vision\naround this idea:"},{"time":135525,"text":"the Atlanta BeltLine, a 22-mile loop"},{"time":138480,"text":"of transit and trails and transformation."},{"time":141746,"text":"I was doing two and three meetings a week\nfor two and a half years,"},{"time":146083,"text":"and so was Cathy and her staff\nand a handful of volunteers."},{"time":149552,"text":"Together, we built this amazing movement\nof people and ideas."},{"time":154287,"text":"It included community advocates\nwho were used to fighting against things,"},{"time":158022,"text":"but found the Atlanta BeltLine\nas something that they could fight for;"},{"time":161359,"text":"developers who saw the opportunity"},{"time":163108,"text":"to take advantage of a lot\nof new growth in the city;"},{"time":166067,"text":"and dozens of nonprofit partners\nwho saw their mission"},{"time":170737,"text":"at least partly accomplished\nby the shared vision."}]},{"cues":[{"time":175293,"text":"Now, usually these groups of people\naren't at the same table"},{"time":179142,"text":"wanting the same outcome."},{"time":181923,"text":"But there we were,\nand it was kind of weird,"},{"time":185318,"text":"but it was really, really powerful."},{"time":187937,"text":"The people of Atlanta\nfell in love with a vision"},{"time":190794,"text":"that was better than what they saw\nthrough their car windshields,"},{"time":194122,"text":"and the people of Atlanta made it happen,"},{"time":196648,"text":"and I guarantee you we would not\nbe building it otherwise."}]},{"cues":[{"time":200476,"text":"From the beginning,\nour coalition was diverse."},{"time":203343,"text":"People of all stripes\nwere part of our story."},{"time":206490,"text":"People on the lower end\nof the economic spectrum loved it, too."},{"time":210330,"text":"They were just afraid\nthey weren't going to be able to be there"},{"time":213544,"text":"when it got built,\nthat they'd be priced out."},{"time":215737,"text":"And we've all heard\nthat kind of story before, right?"},{"time":219852,"text":"But we promised that\nthe Atlanta BeltLine would be different,"},{"time":222938,"text":"and people took ownership of the idea,"},{"time":224996,"text":"and they made it better\nthan anything we ever imagined"},{"time":227594,"text":"in the beginning,"},{"time":228819,"text":"including significant\nsubsidies for housing,"},{"time":231606,"text":"new parks, art, an arboretum --\na list that continues to grow."},{"time":236936,"text":"And we put in place"},{"time":238126,"text":"the organizations and agencies\nthat were required to make it happen."},{"time":241773,"text":"And importantly, it is."}]},{"cues":[{"time":244126,"text":"Now we're in the early stages\nof implementation, and it's working."},{"time":247918,"text":"The first mainline section\nof trail was opened in 2012,"},{"time":252735,"text":"and it's already generated\nover three billion dollars"},{"time":255416,"text":"of private-sector investment."},{"time":258784,"text":"But it's not only changing\nthe physical form of the city,"},{"time":261524,"text":"it's changing the way\nwe think about the city,"},{"time":263958,"text":"and what our expectations are\nfor living there."},{"time":268171,"text":"About a month ago,"},{"time":269838,"text":"I had to take my kids with me\nto the grocery store"},{"time":272697,"text":"and they were complaining about it,"},{"time":274393,"text":"because they didn't want\nto get in the car."},{"time":276465,"text":"They were saying, \"Dad, if we have to go,"},{"time":280489,"text":"can we at least ride our bikes?\""},{"time":282242,"text":"And I said, \"Of course we can."},{"time":284572,"text":"That's what people in Atlanta do."},{"time":286631,"text":"We ride our bikes to the grocery store.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":289074,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":290331,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":291955,"text":"Thank you, yeah."}]},{"cues":[{"time":293234,"text":"Now, they don't know\nhow ridiculous that is,"},{"time":296497,"text":"but I do."},{"time":297684,"text":"And I also understand\nthat their expectations for Atlanta"},{"time":301717,"text":"are really powerful."}]},{"cues":[{"time":303642,"text":"This kind of transformation\nis exactly like sprawl"},{"time":307020,"text":"in the last century,"},{"time":308647,"text":"the movement where our investment\nin highways and automobiles"},{"time":312091,"text":"fundamentally changed American life."},{"time":314686,"text":"That wasn't some grand conspiracy."},{"time":317120,"text":"There were conspiracies\nwithin it, of course."},{"time":320044,"text":"But it was a cultural momentum."},{"time":322161,"text":"It was millions of people\nmaking millions of decisions"},{"time":324754,"text":"over an extended period of time,"},{"time":326370,"text":"that fundamentally changed\nnot only the way that we build cities,"},{"time":330156,"text":"but it changed our expectations"},{"time":332194,"text":"for our lives."},{"time":334613,"text":"These changes were the foundations\nfor urban sprawl."},{"time":337888,"text":"We didn't call it sprawl at that time."},{"time":340026,"text":"We called it the future."},{"time":341577,"text":"And it was."},{"time":342991,"text":"And we got all the highways\nand strip malls and cul-de-sacs we wanted."}]},{"cues":[{"time":347430,"text":"It was a radical transformation,"},{"time":349820,"text":"but it was built by a cultural momentum."},{"time":352457,"text":"So it's important to not separate"},{"time":354055,"text":"the physical construction\nof the places we live"},{"time":356553,"text":"from other things that\nare happening at that time."},{"time":359268,"text":"At that time,"},{"time":360820,"text":"in the second half of the last century,"},{"time":363105,"text":"science was curing disease"},{"time":365121,"text":"and lifting us to the moon,"},{"time":367014,"text":"and the sexual revolution\nwas breaking down barriers,"},{"time":369569,"text":"and the Civil Rights Movement\nbegan its march"},{"time":371705,"text":"toward the fulfillment\nof our nation's promise."},{"time":374664,"text":"Television, entertainment, food, travel,\nbusiness -- everything was changing,"},{"time":379425,"text":"and both the public\nand private sectors were colluding"},{"time":382749,"text":"to give us the lives we wanted."},{"time":386041,"text":"The Federal Highway Administration,"},{"time":387774,"text":"for example, didn't exist\nbefore there were highways."},{"time":391794,"text":"Think about it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":392996,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":394044,"text":"Of course, today it's important\nto understand and acknowledge"},{"time":397055,"text":"that those benefits accrued\nto some groups of people"},{"time":399874,"text":"and not to others."},{"time":401170,"text":"It was not an equitable cultural momentum."},{"time":404692,"text":"But when we look today\nin wonder and disgust, maybe,"},{"time":408382,"text":"at the metropolis sprawl before us,"},{"time":410869,"text":"we wonder if we're stuck."},{"time":413067,"text":"Are we stuck with the legacy\nof that inequity?"},{"time":416234,"text":"Are we stuck with this dystopian\ntraffic hellscape?"},{"time":420329,"text":"Are we stuck with rampant\nurban displacement,"},{"time":423479,"text":"with environmental degradation?"},{"time":426504,"text":"Are we stuck with social isolation"},{"time":429061,"text":"or political polarization?"},{"time":431399,"text":"Are these the inevitable\nand permanent outcomes?"},{"time":434744,"text":"Or are they the result\nof our collective cultural decisions"},{"time":437746,"text":"that we've made for ourselves?"},{"time":440535,"text":"And if they are,"},{"time":442658,"text":"can't we change them?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":444803,"text":"What I have learned\nfrom our experience in Atlanta"},{"time":447461,"text":"is not an anomaly."},{"time":448994,"text":"Similar stories\nare playing out everywhere,"},{"time":451389,"text":"where people are reclaiming\nnot only old railroads,"},{"time":454226,"text":"but also degraded urban waterways\nand obsolete roadways,"},{"time":458109,"text":"reinventing all of the infrastructure"},{"time":460473,"text":"in their lives."},{"time":461836,"text":"Whether here in New York"},{"time":463784,"text":"or in Houston"},{"time":465044,"text":"or Miami,"},{"time":466371,"text":"Detroit, Philadelphia,"},{"time":469058,"text":"Seoul, Hong Kong, Singapore,"},{"time":471394,"text":"Toronto and Paris,"},{"time":473055,"text":"cities big and small all over the world\nare reclaiming and reinventing"},{"time":477207,"text":"this infrastructure for themselves,"},{"time":478904,"text":"including the mother\nof all catalyst infrastructure projects,"},{"time":483489,"text":"the Los Angeles River,"},{"time":485485,"text":"the revitalization effort\nfor which similarly started"},{"time":488279,"text":"as a grassroots movement,"},{"time":489677,"text":"has developed into a cultural momentum,"},{"time":492037,"text":"and is now in the early stages\nof being transformed"},{"time":495503,"text":"into some kind of life-affirming\ninfrastructure again,"},{"time":498832,"text":"this one with trails and parks\nand fishing and boating"},{"time":503251,"text":"and community revitalization,"},{"time":505210,"text":"and of course, water quality\nand flood control."},{"time":508290,"text":"It's already improving\nthe lives of people."},{"time":510794,"text":"It's already changing the way\nthe rest of us think about Los Angeles."}]},{"cues":[{"time":515246,"text":"This is more than just infrastructure."},{"time":517729,"text":"We're building new lives for ourselves."},{"time":520214,"text":"It's a movement that includes\nlocal food, urban agriculture,"},{"time":523792,"text":"craft beer, the maker movement,"},{"time":526062,"text":"tech and design -- all of these things,\nearly indicators of a really radical shift"},{"time":530865,"text":"in the way we build cities."},{"time":533132,"text":"We're taking places like this"},{"time":536534,"text":"and transforming them into this."},{"time":540669,"text":"And soon this."}]},{"cues":[{"time":543063,"text":"And this is all exciting and good."},{"time":546436,"text":"We're changing the world for the better."},{"time":548426,"text":"Good for us!"},{"time":550263,"text":"And it is awesome -- I mean that."},{"time":552956,"text":"But our history of sprawl,"},{"time":554950,"text":"and from what we can already see\nwith these catalyst projects today,"},{"time":558910,"text":"we know and must remember"},{"time":561118,"text":"that big changes like this\ndon't usually benefit everyone."},{"time":564999,"text":"The market forces unleashed\nby this cultural momentum"},{"time":568574,"text":"often include the seemingly unstoppable"},{"time":571023,"text":"and inevitable cycle of rising taxes,\nprices and rents."}]},{"cues":[{"time":575933,"text":"This is urgent."},{"time":577332,"text":"If we care, we have to stand up"},{"time":579498,"text":"and speak out."},{"time":580839,"text":"This should be a call to action,"},{"time":582646,"text":"because the answer can't be\nto not improve communities."},{"time":586717,"text":"The answer can't be to not build parks\nand transit and grocery stores."},{"time":591215,"text":"The answer can't be\nto hold communities down"},{"time":594152,"text":"just to keep them affordable."},{"time":596523,"text":"But we do have to follow through\nand address the financial realities"},{"time":599824,"text":"that we're facing."},{"time":601078,"text":"This is hard, and it won't\nhappen on its own."},{"time":603897,"text":"We can do it, and I'm committed\nto this goal in Atlanta,"},{"time":606794,"text":"to sticking up again for people\nwho made it possible in the first place."},{"time":611520,"text":"We can't call it a success without them."},{"time":614105,"text":"I certainly can't,"},{"time":615436,"text":"because the people I made\ncommitments to all those years"},{"time":618392,"text":"weren't abstract populations."},{"time":620615,"text":"They're my friends and neighbors."},{"time":622459,"text":"They're people that I love."}]},{"cues":[{"time":624974,"text":"So even though it started\nas my graduate thesis"},{"time":627532,"text":"and I'm working hard for 16 years\nwith thousands of people"},{"time":630528,"text":"to help make this thing come to life,"},{"time":632702,"text":"I know and believe that who\nthe BeltLine is being built for"},{"time":636643,"text":"is just as important\nas whether it's built at all."},{"time":640065,"text":"Not just in Atlanta,"},{"time":641944,"text":"but locally and globally,"},{"time":643437,"text":"we have to understand"},{"time":645606,"text":"this accountability to the people\nwhose lives we are changing,"},{"time":649287,"text":"because this is us."},{"time":651418,"text":"We are the lives we're talking about."},{"time":654431,"text":"These places aren't inevitable."},{"time":656092,"text":"The places we live aren't inevitable,"},{"time":658797,"text":"and if we want something different,\nwe just need to speak up."},{"time":661839,"text":"We have to ensure that change\ncomes on our terms."},{"time":664437,"text":"And to do that,"},{"time":665616,"text":"we have to participate actively\nin the process of shaping change."}]},{"cues":[{"time":670547,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":671723,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}